descriptionHtml:
[center][color=RED][size=+2]The Cultists Robes Retexture[/size][/center][/color]

[size=+1]
[center]Simply a retexture of the cultists robes.[/center]


[IMG]http://i1273.photobucket.com/albums/y401/Andre7890/ScreenShot124_zps0fdbdecb.jpg[/IMG]


Vanilla\'s texture

[IMG]http://i1273.photobucket.com/albums/y401/Andre7890/ScreenShot129_zps9b153b70.jpg[/IMG]


New Textures

[IMG]http://i1273.photobucket.com/albums/y401/Andre7890/ScreenShot126_zpsdf33a35c.jpg[/IMG]


[center]Install: just drop \"Textures\" folder into \"Textures\" folder in your Skyrim\\Data.[/center]

[center]Please leave a comment if you have any suggest, if you like or if you don\'t like something.[/center]

[center]If you like it, you can also try my [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/30173]Necromancer Amulet Retexture[/url], [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/32561]Bones and Skeletons Retexture[/url], [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/32449]The Miraak Retexture[/url], [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/31731]The Divine Amulets Retexture[/url] and [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/32182]The Divine Shrines Retexture[/url].[/center][/size]

[center][color=RED][size=+1]It\'s not free for other\'s Conversion, neither Upload on any other sites.
Do not upload anywhere include Steam workshop without my Permission.[/size][/color][/center]


[center]Andrea[/center][/size]
